	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It doesn't have to look like a SNES game to be glitch free. It is perfectly possible to have a status bar and multidirectional scrolling on the NES without glitches, but you have to spend some calibrating the timing to make sure it's solid, and professional developers back in the day had deadlines that prevented them from spending time fixing things like these.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
